      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from certified coupon testing of Ti-6Al-4V ELI lot material; geometric inputs from CMM measurements of test articles.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and tangent modulus (2.2 GPa) derived from tensile coupon tests on the same material lot as the test constructs. Geometry inputs confirmed by CMM measurements on three representative screws with < 0.02 mm deviation from nominal CAD."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
